es/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b87be9250b57dc404154cf032bdd7c3e90db12","tid":439642,"uid":38030,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T09:21:55.000Z","msg":"寧願早三個字起身搭巴士都唔搭地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db87f11ddcb361fe9f3565439aca1cb88938013a","tid":439642,"uid":140094,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T09:25:49.000Z","msg":"搭地鐵好煩<br />\n企入去唔想後面d人上唔到車既時候<br />\n落車個陣又要諗點突破d人群 唔知落唔落到<br />\n無哂扶手驚架車突然chok會仆街<br />\n有得坐既話又唔知會唔會見到老人家同大肚婆<br />\n有時繁忙時間揹住書包又驚撞到或者整到其他人<br />\n諗諗下都係貴d搭巴士舒服d算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b01c1a9e6bc157d569081fd3a735b250664d5b0d","tid":439642,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T09:28:51.000Z","msg":"有時巴士去唔到焗坐地鐵"},{"pid":"ceb4431e883e3b44c1a4c5d9d918564f93c13bf2","tid":439642,"uid":43350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T09:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又迫又焗又臭,尤其觀塘線d車,有陣豬餿味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今日上車,我係門口企,<br />\n已經好逼冇位<br />\n個呀伯死都要逼入黎 又要撞到人 批到我手<br />\n都唔知咁趕住去做乜 幾廿歲人係到逼係到趕?<br />\n重點係佢臭撚到仆街<br />\n聞到勁想嘔 勁暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n地鐵冷氣風吹埋黎真係..........."},{"pid":"83bc3c2304c8f02625320c535b32bc91f6b44116","tid":439642,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T10:03:04.000Z","msg":"鬼叫窮咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n企足粒幾鐘先到屋企"},{"pid":"a2ec9ca47c13bc8ec64cdf34b997fb2b50689276","tid":439642,"uid":117786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T10:14:03.000Z","msg":"好逼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f2ddc37d5ec73737e2b8fdd984c2be0db97bee","tid":439642,"uid":24227,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T10:27:06.000Z","msg":"一向唔鐘意<br />\n豬籠車咁 <br />\n返工焗搭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3360b17c04fca625b15e95b9f322edf1d9a850ca","tid":439642,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T10:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭地鐵好煩<br />\n企入去唔想後面d人上唔到車既時候<br />\n落車個陣又要諗點突破d人群 唔知落唔落到<br />\n無哂扶手驚架車突然chok會仆街<br />\n有得坐既話又唔知會唔會見到老人家同大肚婆<br />\n有時繁忙時間揹住書包又驚撞到或者整到其他人<br />\n諗諗下都係貴d搭巴士舒服d算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下個站落就企出d<br />\n由d人迫入去 <br />\n企硬<br />\n迫入去衰硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ead590fa81599e11fc9638ef4833129e0c6fff","tid":439642,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T10:47:04.000Z","msg":"咩巴士又脫班有塞車<br />\n狗鐵又全日都迫撚到死<br />\n小巴唔係總站又上唔到車<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567dbdbff2fe6bf15db2fd08d84e73ea24952f0d","tid":439642,"uid":34490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T10:50:12.000Z","msg":"啱啱相反<br />\n屌你老味d巴士班次又少又疏<br />\n勁難預時間 <br />\n打去投訴又話要一個月了解 正仆街"},{"pid":"99601bcd2bd33150c0198a8d9ce010c7e8517d37","tid":439642,"uid":29489,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T10:54:09.000Z","msg":"我調轉<br />\n<br />\n巴士佬d 風琴腳好辛苦<br />\n班次又唔準時<br />\n十次有九次準時係無用<br />\n因為唔準時果次係一鋪過還晒<br />\n<br />\n有