":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T11:52:11.000Z","msg":"啱啊！"},{"pid":"ef528b4138ab23ae1841cd9cade2431f02d9a4ca","tid":439642,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T12:04:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>d 支制車一陣臭膠味<br />\n都唔知有無毒</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45edb4b8c0bf379e005b72c29539c267fe584551","tid":439642,"uid":25221,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T12:06:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79ff3eaf021dd2abd7bccd387531b7eb31565fe1","tid":439642,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T12:16:39.000Z","msg":"講逼又唔夠東京逼<br />\n講熱又唔夠倫敦熱<br />\n講臭又唔夠巴黎臭<br />\n咁嘅價是但啦<br />\n利申：平時搭巴士"},{"pid":"33d1c5c56687a16c76a806977d938e196f3012bb","tid":439642,"uid":22316,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T12:29:24.000Z","msg":"搭地鐵好多人都無咩公徳心<br />\n返工返學時間 最撚多人既時候又挨住個扶手<br />\n入車廂個陣 啲人又唔理排隊既次序<br />\n架車一到又衝入車廂 <br />\n有次試過放工時間係金鐘到等車 <br />\n明明架車已經勁逼 仲有個女人老撚都要塞入車 個袋又大<br />\n道門又夾到佢個袋 又再彈開 累到全世界人都要再同佢一齊再等<br />\n講左句等多班車先上洗死咩 又即刻黑面 <br />\n之後等緊下班車既我 有架空車開過嚟 坐住返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be272a7b8eb740e843783dcc0e73550bf16bb4b","tid":439642,"uid":12741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T12:30:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴士服務愈黎愈好 而且係巴士瞓一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n臨到站會自動醒</blockquote><br />\n有得訓真係差好遠<br />\n<br />\n我愛巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99c40dca5fff0573907a34eeb930f5dd888207b","tid":439642,"uid":125079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T12:34:33.000Z","msg":"地鐵繁忙時間真係好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ac970791ed319b2a561ae369635c58b864503f","tid":439642,"uid":50018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-