br />\n<br />\n我愛巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係非繁忙時間由我屋企出發<br />\n坐巴士快過碌地鐵<br />\n唔塞車嘅話 返工時間都係差唔多<br />\n如果兩種交通工具坐是但一樣唔洗錢<br />\n我會揀坐巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c611621860189196304654c9ea0ea6c2a048005","tid":439642,"uid":67212,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:17:55.000Z","msg":"地鐵無咩問題<br />\n火車正垃圾"},{"pid":"918dd9d04797c2df363dd98d5bb94cac4f36d4e2","tid":439642,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:26:43.000Z","msg":"觀塘線都係唔好搭為妙，真係有毒，要經呢條線就改搭巴士"},{"pid":"b389cf7b172b8139d3d2a9992476a5e2d948d555","tid":439642,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:27:24.000Z","msg":"從來冇鐘意過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a1f4a93ffdaec0aded821ea778580a1a763e7d","tid":439642,"uid":9171,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:28:54.000Z","msg":"應該得鐵膠先會鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c911e3d21b2cbfac420a711750530dc35ffcd16","tid":439642,"uid":41614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:30:15.000Z","msg":"觀塘線特別多窮人廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以成陣臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我係其中一個窮人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"157cd08737b56e5149a55f674959f542d0957ed5","tid":439642,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:31:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67f71a73b2493a8b49ebf19f7c4ee9452f192adb","tid":439642,"uid":104723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:35:37.000Z","msg":"唔鍾意搭<br />\n但佢又快又平過巴士 無得唔搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad30a77be0de4e7c58d7deabf11ad7029acdb35b","tid":439642,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:37:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔鍾意搭<br />\n但佢又快又<span style=\"color: red;\">平過巴士</span> 無得唔搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學生啫 <br />\n快係講穩定"},{"pid":"dc0e8fb0d82397df074890bec445415d5dceedb5","tid":439642,"uid":10968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:38:06.000Z","msg":"唔洗轉車既話點都會首選巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9526359bf2861f8cf6b4b97ab162d3a3e32fb9","tid":439642,"uid":52636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:38:07.000Z","msg":"特別經過九龍塘"},{"pid":"d50d7167539fd95a97604ddee07bb2ddc3e7bd98","tid":439642,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:39:21.000Z","msg":"鍾意坐巴士"},{"pid":"3c98c54cdf87618d492153d2119b8a165833de8f","tid":439642,"uid":105552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:40:41.000Z","msg":"依家操大隻有部份都為左搭地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD人都癡撚線 唔好話廢中廢老<br />\n有D後生著著西裝好眉好貌見到人未落哂都急急腳塞入黎<br />\n根本成個香港都係咁既生態"},{"pid":"385b41dc8558503bb59b026fa44fc6cf811b71f7","tid":439642,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:42:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鍾意坐巴士</blockquote><br />\n平，又唔洗轉車，又有位坐，又訓得舒服<br />\n地鐵無野比得上"},{"pid":"3c012e459ba9b9ab32ac21450f9aab09e7f17ebc","tid":439642,"uid":75195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:45:12.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母 依家欣澳上地鐵既九成都係蝗黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22556d691d32f6dc02fd334d077927986378f5cd","tid":439642,"uid":37101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:45:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有其他車答邊個會想迫地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n答你老母"},{"pid":"dc5b09e7e0f3502da21405bfb7a84b965784bc91","tid":439642,"uid":8012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:49:47.000Z","msg":"又熱又焗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdadd94f6e4ff78879e0905163231c8c3deb3e9f","tid":439642,"uid":22431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:59:29.000Z","msg":"嗌極都唔企入啲 仲有位攤大份報紙睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa86a91e1ff6d53325a3fcfa69153ee68ae23d4","tid":439642,"uid":120801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:00:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以買左車，寧願塞車都唔迫地鐵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一塞車時內急都要係車上解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa33f6fd46de0e1636a76fdfe16197885bfc70f","tid":439642,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:08:40.000Z","msg":"所有人轉搭巴士，<br />\n一來路面車少左就唔會塞<br />\n二來一上車即時瘋狂訓覺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：揸車返工"},{"pid":"5ba116a9d644e808a056bdafd24a0cf6ac4e0d32","tid":439642,"uid":118553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:10:23.000Z","msg":"係趕時間同地鐵站近目的地先會搭地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係繁忙時間搭等幾班車同開閂門幾次有時真係同搭巴士差唔多咁耐<br />\n有得揀盡量都會搭行路面嘅車，有得坐，最緊要係有得睇景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a789f84e3ee353a5f38fa4ca74ba8102fd95b2","tid":439642,"uid":45821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:12:33.000Z","msg":"繁忙時間個車箱仲焗過佢老母個臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4e2337edb4179aa4a35eec6fb89f292ffe165e","tid":439642,"uid":130474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:18:55.000Z","msg":"根本地鐵成個系統都已超負荷....<br />\n<br />\n路線越來越長, 位越來越少....遲下得返關愛座....<br />\n<br />\n咩都死...."},{"pid":"43ea87caf5ce036fbcd4a2b8a7c3a35587e42fab","tid":439642,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:22:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又迫又焗又臭,尤其觀塘線d車,有陣豬餿味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人本身係臭㗎啦 所以公共場所咪 要開到啲冷氣咁強勁囉<br />\n唔係周圍冤崩爛臭點做生意呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n地鐵 就你得你死呀 還掂你係咪都要搭㗎啦"},{"pid":"f75f6d1f07db0c1652cf603905b105d771d7d18c","tid":439642,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:26:50.000Z","msg":"我平時返學放學嗰架巴士半個鐘一班，日日都會預好時間準時搭佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要快過地鐵，直屌公路<br />\n<br />\n真係預錯時間先會搭地鐵"},{"pid":"d30d1b7fcd31096d7ec82a851ae0102e325ab391","tid":439642,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:28:40.000Z","msg":"搭地鐵有時唔想㩒電話，隻眼唔知望去邊好，周圍望又驚俾人以為我睥佢<br />\n<br />\n搭巴士就睇電話又得，睇街景又得"},{"pid":"2b2ab5f13096b01cd983d163cd0bbe0248e80d88","tid":439642,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:34:36.000Z","msg":"火車臭撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa81b79350a0f3762ee68942780eaf9700291ee","tid":439642,"uid":117032,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:45:58.000Z","msg":"豬餿味?好彩冇同你同車啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67e5de70cc348ce63efb88f9eadc994764ce0298","tid":439642,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T15:37:21.000Z","msg":"東鐵線火車好撚污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又多拖喼蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8fa4f9b8ad0b04f1c3112775df4a6ef22e20523","tid":439642,"uid":133743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T15:51:16.000Z","msg":"其實而家非繁忙時間都好多人"},{"pid":"e4e1d5b6fc77c4d6cec2ac7350981b9163d95c8a","tid":439642,"uid":7937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T15:53:02.000Z","msg":"不嬲唔鍾意搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過唔鍾意又可以點 咪又係要搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d149a61b7f89dfaaeb47999664a71d9db9f90f2c","tid":439642,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T16:14:10.000Z","msg":"返工地鐵 收工巴士"},{"pid":"c333d0d52faf65c5b73b90508831af269f9e62b3","tid":439642,"uid":51484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T16:18:54.000Z","msg":"從來都無鍾意過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d45a83cce550bed84d48e20a284a5fe3f76155b","tid":439642,"uid":85591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T16:21:54.000Z","msg":"你試下日日搭東鐵線, 遲早要入青山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f3242f0989cc20cf58fef4265cc07c088932b4","tid":439642,"uid":61914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T16:22:16.000Z","msg":"憎到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa7437e9ce593019a65c7eac3838340093f68e5","tid":439642,"uid":102171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T16:27:19.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇人覺得經過奧運站車廂一開門成日都會有陣臭味 同埋唔係講笑 有時返工放工多人車廂逼果陣一定有陣放屁味好臭 透唔到氣咁滯"},{"pid":"9296f11a6f646ae3bdbb4e8706d46a64df90ea79","tid":439642,"uid":117786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T00:29:47.000Z","msg":"香港人生十大酷殘之一，一定係日日搭地鐵番工放工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37fee7e8265f7493c532428147121d742242711e","tid":439642,"uid":22227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T00:45:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edbe173cba47a1c74572a529e45ef16193591576","tid":439642,"uid":126648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T00:54:49.000Z","msg":"巴士咪一樣"},{"pid":"5010b132de629ea545e41e8d27a23427c3c9723f","tid":439642,"uid":129877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T00:55:43.000Z","msg":"都唔知點解逼極都仲有位上"},{"pid":"754934ee679f71d2d104337b7c0b5261e4944527","tid":439642,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T01:11:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鐘意坐巴士。可以望下風景。<br />\n不過等車等好耐<br />\n所以返工坐地鐵，放工坐巴士</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴士繁忙時間好多都要企，仲要迫<br />\n企巴士迫巴士，仲辛苦企地鐵迫地鐵<br />\n司機轉灣，或突然停車，成班人就hihi"},{"pid":"a5c08386ea1f48739b1a3866a36026948b00ff13","tid":439642,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T01:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <blockquote>搭地鐵有時唔想㩒電話，隻眼唔知望去邊好，周圍望又驚俾人以為我睥佢<br />\n<br />\n搭巴士就睇電話又得，睇街景又得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我覺得搭巴士，睇手機好暈。<br />\n搭地鐵，睇手機方便，唔暈。<br />\n<br />\n地鐵冇風景睇，唔睇手機，悶，對眼冇咁好。<br />\n東鐵，西鐵，東涌線，南港島線就冇呢個問題。<br />\n<br />\n鐵路，始終是比較，準時，冇塞車問題，班次密，安全，冇交通意外。用電，較用燃油環保。同埋要上上落落，迫你做多些運動。我唔專登出街行，淨返工，都行左幾千步。<br />\n<br />\n巴士，就舒服少少，有風景睇，多數有位座，點到點。但就唔安全，唔準時，唔環保。"},{"pid":"992575fd9a79a7feb5a6dc5c5518488ccce12d81","tid":439642,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T01:33:23.000Z","msg":"有得揀就唔搭"}]}